com.inmobi.messaging.instrumentation
Class PintailTimingAccumulator

java.lang.Object
  com.inmobi.messaging.instrumentation.PintailTimingAccumulator

public class PintailTimingAccumulator
extends Object

Store a cumulative stats for invocation of some piece of code. Note that only usage convention governs the semantics of values stored in here. This is not meant to be AOP style code that does the actual magic. (cumulativeNanoseconds / successCount) can be used to figure out mean time spent under normal circumstances i.e. free of unhandled exceptions
